# Module: `packages/utils`

- General-purpose helpers only — keep functions small and focused
- Prefer pure functions; avoid stateful utilities

## How to verify

- `grep -r "let\|useState\|useRef" packages/utils/` — stateful patterns should be absent
- Each exported function should have a single clear responsibility — review on code review
- `yarn build:packages` — confirms no broken imports
